One Acre, founded in 2006, supplies smallholder farmers with the agricultural services they need to make their farms more productive. We provide quality farm supplies on credit, delivered within walking distance of farmers’ homes, and agricultural trainings to improve harvests. We measure our success by our ability to make farmers more prosperous: On average, farmers harvest 50 percent more food after working with One Acre Fund. We serve more than 800,000 farm families in Eastern and Southern Africa, with more than 7,500 full-time staff, and we aim to serve 1 million farm families by 2020. We are recruiting to fill the following positions below: Location: Kenya Deadline: 10th January, 2021. Click Here to Read Job Details & Apply Location: Niger Deadline: 18th November, 2020. Click Here to Read Job Details & Apply Location: Rwanda Deadline: 3rd December, 2020. Click Here to Read Job Details & Apply Location: Niger Deadline: 2nd December, 2020. Click Here to Read Job Details & Apply The post Submit CVs – New Recruitment at One Acre Fund appeared first on Jobs in Nigeria – http://jobsinnigeria.careers. Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.